name: III. FLOR MAIOR (BIG FLOWER)
description:
It rescues the strength of the feminine as the image and likeness of the divine through the sacred triad, where the first light originated in creation is the seed, from which everything derives and is built, generating awareness of existence. The woman, the generative, has the power to create all forms of life, initially the spirits as well as all of nature.

This artwork is from a limited edition of 20 prints
Printed in UltraChrome HDx mineral pigment - Epson
420x594mm Hahnemühle Museum Etching 350g
Rafael Prado - Brazil - 2020
